{
  "stem": "23131.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So you had to sell something from the house, or to take something and exchange with somebody.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it wasn't easy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the missus needed everything the best for her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If it was something in the house, she was the first one-- she and her son.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Her son took a liking to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's true.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe this was the reason that she was afraid that something shouldn't come out of it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This-- the-- the slaughter was May 8th, in the end of June.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "During June, when Tovia heard the whole story of what's going on--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--with-- with the-- it was May 8th.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was-- in fact, he was in-- in-- he wasn't in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he was in Lida when this happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he sent somebody to tell us, and begged my father to get out from-- from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father said, absolutely no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the ghetto, we used to get together, you know, in somebody's yard at night, until-- until the time that we were allowed to in the ghetto, and sing the-- of-- oh, yeah-- each one of us belonged-- not each one.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't belong.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My parents didn't allow me-- to some kind of a party, you know, like the Zionists, like the Betar, like-- and sing the songs from-- from once upon a time, and think what will be tomorrow?",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Go home and pray to God that tonight should nothing happen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One night-- it was in the end of June-- I came from one of my girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she gave me her jacket to throw on me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I came home, and I get undressed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I got to bed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I hear somebody is patting me on the shoulder.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
